WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:06.206
Hey, good morning, family. How are y'all doing today? I have some things on my heart to share with you.

00:00:06.207 --> 00:00:10.198
First off, I just want to say thank you for all your support. God bless you all.

00:00:10.199 --> 00:00:20.576
Thank you from the bottom of our hearts; we just want to say thank you for all the beautiful things that you all have said.

00:00:20.578 --> 00:00:29.693
You know, there are a lot of good emails. I've had over 70,000 emails in the last week, and it's a little overwhelming for us.

00:00:29.694 --> 00:00:35.234
If I seem cranky in the comment section or anything, I apologize. I have been bombarded by a lot.

00:00:35.235 --> 00:00:42.807
We're doing the best we can, but it doesn't give me the right to be cranky sometimes. I just want to say forgive me if I have been.

00:00:42.808 --> 00:00:49.025
There's a lot of the world on here, and there are a lot of people that are very hateful and very rude to us.

00:00:49.026 --> 00:00:56.319
God bless you all, the ones that are rude; we pray for you. We truly do.

00:00:56.320 --> 00:01:10.795
The Lord tells me, 'You've got to walk in love,'and I'm like, 'Wow.'Like I said, if they turn the channel off tomorrow, you can find me on our other YouTube channel. If you want to subscribe to that, it's Come Thrift with Me.

00:01:10.796 --> 00:01:25.193
We did it because my wife likes to thrift, and we like to flip things on eBay and Poshmark and other platforms like that, like Facebook Marketplace or whatever we can do—that's how we make our living.

00:01:25.194 --> 00:01:32.207
We've been doing it for like 11 years now, and God's been faithful. We've built a good business out of it.

00:01:32.208 --> 00:01:38.369
A lot of people go, 'Well, are you doing YouTube for that?'No, I do YouTube because God called me to.

00:01:38.370 --> 00:01:46.108
My business and what I do for a living is Poshmark and eBay. I've been doing that for a long time, and God has been faithful.

00:01:46.109 --> 00:01:52.780
So, if you want to follow us on our Come Thrift with Me channel, it'll be a blessing.

00:01:52.781 --> 00:01:56.699
If anything happens and they shut this down—which I don't know if they will or not—but okay.

00:01:56.700 --> 00:02:00.278
First off, I just want to tell you all what happened at church on Sunday.

00:02:00.279 --> 00:02:05.807
I was standing in the back like I always do, and I was praying during the service.

00:02:05.808 --> 00:02:12.073
The service was outstanding. By the way, we had a special guest speaker there: Mark Hankins was there.

00:02:12.074 --> 00:02:19.279
Powerful man of God, moves in the gifts of the Spirit with signs and wonders, and it was awesome.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:29.483
You all can go on his archives and watch the service on Sunday night and it will bless you at the Glorious Church Fellowship, I believe, YouTube channel.

00:02:29.484 --> 00:02:33.357
It might be there. You can watch it if you want to help support it.

00:02:33.358 --> 00:02:40.253
It's amazing; it would bless your life. Mark Hankins was there Sunday morning and Sunday night.

00:02:40.254 --> 00:02:51.903
So I was standing in the back praying like I always do, and all of a sudden the Lord opened my eyes in the realm of the spirit and I saw an open heaven over that congregation.

00:02:51.904 --> 00:03:01.353
I saw the Lord Jesus sitting up there, and He was watching the service. I could see the great cloud of witnesses watching.

00:03:01.355 --> 00:03:08.617
I could see them; they were peeking out over this portal over the church and they were watching.

00:03:08.618 --> 00:03:18.255
Oh my gosh, the presence of the Lord was so strong. I just sat in the back and wept because I could feel the presence of the Holy Spirit.

00:03:18.256 --> 00:03:24.399
I'm telling you, if you're dry, if you're thirsty, what a place to go.

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:31.837
Then all of a sudden, the Lord showed me a C-17. It's one of the big army planes.

00:03:31.838 --> 00:03:40.537
It's a C-17, I believe, is what it is—one of those big planes that hold all of the major military stuff.

00:03:40.538 --> 00:03:52.399
All of a sudden, that plane—I believe it's a C-17—I saw the plane swoop in and start dropping stuff out of the back of this plane in the spirit.

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:58.871
Healings, anything that you've been believing for, the Lord said He's bringing it.

00:03:58.872 --> 00:04:07.423
Do not lose faith in believing for your miracle. Believe that all things are possible to him that believes.

00:04:07.424 --> 00:04:12.798
We are in the last of the last seconds before the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:04:12.799 --> 00:04:19.149
People say, 'Oh, I've heard that all my life.'I'm trying to warn you that Jesus is coming.

00:04:19.150 --> 00:04:27.673
Even like people say, 'Well, you say that it's been a year or two years, whatever,'on the scope of time, we're talking thousands of years, folks.

00:04:27.674 --> 00:04:32.206
If it's 10 years, that's nothing. How fast does a year go now?

00:04:32.207 --> 00:04:38.951
It's like a snap of a finger. We're already almost going into the last half of the year.

00:04:38.952 --> 00:04:44.949
We have August, September, October, November, December, and then 2024 is done. Look how fast.

00:04:44.950 --> 00:04:49.211
I don't know if the year went by fast for you all, but it went by very fast for me so far.

00:04:49.212 --> 00:04:54.815
So, I'm telling you, time is accelerating and we are on the verge of a major outpouring.

00:04:54.816 --> 00:04:59.506
I'm telling you, I believe with all my heart that we're going to have a great harvest of souls.

00:04:59.507 --> 00:05:10.493
I'm believing for a billion-soul harvest into the kingdom of God. A great harvest of God's people coming into the kingdom.

00:05:10.494 --> 00:05:24.628
So back to the vision: I saw that big plane dropping all those packages and things that people were believing for—demonstrations and manifestations of His glory all over the people.

00:05:24.629 --> 00:05:29.980
And I'm telling you, He told me creative miracles are happening right now in this atmosphere.

00:05:29.981 --> 00:05:34.545
He said, 'Brandon, people that have autoimmune disease are being healed right now.'I could see it.

00:05:34.546 --> 00:05:40.841
And the Lord told me autoimmune disease is being healed; I saw fibromyalgia being healed last night.

00:05:40.842 --> 00:05:45.546
I want to encourage people that God is going to meet you right where you are.

00:05:45.547 --> 00:05:54.766
If you're believing for your miracle, if you're believing for a touch for your finances or whatever, I believe today is your day for your great turnaround.

00:05:54.767 --> 00:05:59.444
I believe today is your day for your miracle of your healing.

00:05:59.445 --> 00:06:15.226
If the symptoms started with pain or whatever, why can't the beginning of your miracle start with the absence of the pain, the discomfort, or the poverty being gone?

00:06:15.227 --> 00:06:20.079
It could change just like that. Just as the symptoms came on, they're gone.

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:22.774
That's what's going to happen. I'm telling you, it's going to be a turnaround.

00:06:22.775 --> 00:06:28.263
And I believe with all my heart, faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:06:28.264 --> 00:06:34.952
And it's your time for your manifestation. God is no respecter of persons, and what He'll do for one, He'll do for another.

00:06:34.952 --> 00:06:42.756
It just takes faith, and you just got to reach out by faith and grab on to what the Lord has for you.

00:06:42.757 --> 00:06:52.568
Number two of what I felt in my heart to tell you all: I was praying, not last night, but Saturday night.

00:06:52.569 --> 00:07:01.598
Saturday night I got a call from Chris Reed. Amazing man of God, one of the most humble people I've ever talked to on the phone.

00:07:01.599 --> 00:07:08.406
I promise y'all, and I don't say that flippantly because I'm not trying to name-drop.

00:07:08.407 --> 00:07:18.133
This guy is a genuine man of God; he loves the Lord, and it was an honor to be able to talk to somebody like him. So, I was on the phone with him and I was praying.

00:07:18.134 --> 00:07:22.239
We prayed together; he said he was praying for me and just wanted to let me know he was lifting me up in prayer.

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:29.671
Well, I got off the phone with him and I was sitting there interceding, and the Lord downloaded to me.

00:07:29.672 --> 00:07:59.750
He said, 'Brandon, I want you to go back to Dana Coverstone's prophetic word—his dream that he had about the covered wagon.'I went back and listened to it immediately when the Lord spoke to me, and I started listening to everything he was saying in that dream about the covered wagon, the rocking of it, and Kamala Harris on the wagon and Joe Biden being on the donkey behind her.

00:07:59.751 --> 00:08:08.611
They were hitting the donkey and Joe Biden fell off. It didn't make it sound like he went home; the way it sounded to me was...

00:08:08.612 --> 00:08:16.193
Hillary came up beside her, and she had a thing on Trump's neck with a big key on it, with mold on it and everything.

00:08:16.194 --> 00:08:22.223
Go listen to that prophetic dream; I believe that was four years off.

00:08:22.224 --> 00:08:29.082
I believe we're seeing it manifest right now. Go listen to it.

00:08:29.083 --> 00:08:36.505
It's going to freak you all out because, as I said, if it doesn't happen within that time frame, everyone says, "Oh, he's a false prophet.

00:08:36.506 --> 00:08:44.199
Dana Coverstone's weird."No, go back and listen to it. God's timing is perfect.

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:52.792
We all thought there were a lot of people that gave words about 2020 that said Trump was going to be in office.

00:08:52.793 --> 00:08:58.419
When the Lord told me, "Brandon, he's not going to be president in 2020,"I had so much hate from people.

00:08:58.420 --> 00:09:04.140
In fact, I had friends who didn't want to talk to me anymore. They got really mad at me and said, "You're missing it.

00:09:04.141 --> 00:09:21.793
You're not hearing God."And I said, "The Lord spoke to me and told me that this is not going to manifest, that Joe Biden will run the country for the timeframe."And then I saw him being removed and that Kamala Harris would step in.

00:09:21.794 --> 00:09:26.923
Some people say, "Well, he wasn't removed all the way. He's still in office."They don't even know where he's at right now.

00:09:26.924 --> 00:09:39.475
Maybe at this time in this video, they said he falsified the signature on the document, and they underlined it, saying the signatures don't match up, saying that it's not even him that signed the piece of paper, saying that he wasn't going to run anymore.

00:09:39.476 --> 00:09:43.756
There are a lot of conspiracies out there right now. So I'm just like, what's really going on?

00:09:43.757 --> 00:09:51.836
Because I told you all, and this is what I think is interesting: I told you all to watch Michelle, to watch Gavin.

00:09:51.837 --> 00:09:57.424
I've warned you. I don't know how many times I've seen Michelle Obama and Gavin.

00:09:57.425 --> 00:10:05.119
Hillary is who I thought. I said, "I saw a woman with short, sandy blonde hair.

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:08.187
It was right in here on her head, and the Lord blotted her face.

00:10:08.188 --> 00:10:12.906
He would not allow me to see that."Why? I have no idea. This is what the Lord did.

00:10:12.907 --> 00:10:20.841
And I saw them hit her going beside Kamala Harris going clear up into January.

00:10:20.842 --> 00:10:31.975
So, I see in part. This is just me adding my intellect to this word right now.

00:10:31.976 --> 00:10:35.573
I told you exactly what I saw, but this is just me thinking now.

00:10:35.574 --> 00:10:48.398
Don't say, "Well, you said this."No, just listen to me. What if Kamala Harris is with Hillary?

00:10:48.399 --> 00:10:54.479
Because Hillary came out immediately with Bill and endorsed Kamala Harris.

00:10:54.480 --> 00:11:01.633
Then Joe—from what I understand, people are telling me that Barack Obama said, "No, not so fast.

00:11:01.634 --> 00:11:22.879
This has to be voted on at the Democratic caucus."Well, if she ends up taking it—if she doesn't take it and they don't get her in—is he planning to do something with Kamala?

00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:29.725
Is he planning to do something with Michelle and maybe Gavin in the future? I don't know.

00:11:29.726 --> 00:11:40.769
But I've told you all I've prayed over that for over two years now, that I saw her running with Gavin.

00:11:40.770 --> 00:11:50.423
They were a force to be reckoned with. People go, "Well, it's a shoo-in."No. If Michelle and Gavin go, it is. We've got to pray.

00:11:50.424 --> 00:11:57.412
It's like some people say, "Well, we've got a little bit of victory here, and we can see the finish line."It's like the tortoise and the hare.

00:11:57.413 --> 00:12:04.466
The hare goes, "Man, I've got this race,"and he goes over there and he lays down and takes a nap because he thinks he can beat that tortoise.

00:12:04.467 --> 00:12:14.259
And the tortoise is going, "I think I can. I think I can."He's tripping over himself and he's falling, and the hare is over there sleeping.

00:12:14.260 --> 00:12:29.792
All of a sudden, the tortoise gets ahead of the hare, and the whole story everyone knows: the tortoise wins and the hare loses because he got overconfident in his ability to win.

00:12:29.793 --> 00:12:39.941
Do not let your guard down spiritually just because you think we have won. We have got to take the enemy camp seriously.

00:12:39.942 --> 00:12:51.083
And I'm not calling the Democrats the enemy; I'm talking about the principalities and powers and the rulers over the darkness and spiritual wickedness in high places.

00:12:51.084 --> 00:12:55.905
We wrestle not against flesh and blood, ladies and gentlemen, but against those things.

00:12:55.906 --> 00:13:00.864
The Bible's told us that. So, I never label a human being as an enemy, ever.

00:13:00.865 --> 00:13:05.754
But I'm talking about the demonic forces right now. That's what I'm trying to say.

00:13:05.755 --> 00:13:14.200
Never let your guard down on your enemy, ever. That's the devil. He has a plan to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:13:14.201 --> 00:13:19.214
But the Bible says that Jesus came that we might have life and life more abundantly.

00:13:19.215 --> 00:13:29.905
I'm just saying a lot of the theologies line up with the dark side.

00:13:29.906 --> 00:13:36.958
And I'm not saying all the Republican side is always light, but they have a tendency to sway good.

00:13:36.959 --> 00:13:41.922
Never stop and be the hare laying down so the tortoise can win.

00:13:41.923 --> 00:13:52.462
Even when we have the upper hand spiritually and we see that victory finish line, don't let your guard down.

00:13:52.463 --> 00:13:58.714
I always say—this is going to be a gross illustration—but it's like an old dead dog in the road.

00:13:58.715 --> 00:14:07.342
You keep running it over until it's a greasy spot. You've got to keep going over it.

00:14:07.343 --> 00:14:13.168
That's probably a gross illustration, but you keep hitting that devil until he's a greasy spot.

00:14:13.169 --> 00:14:26.011
Don't give up when you see the first blade of your miracle. You need the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation of the whole fruit of the corn. Do not give up on this.

00:14:26.012 --> 00:14:42.153
It's time for us to put our shields up even stronger and stand up even greater than what we ever had before, believing for a turnaround of our nation, to believe for things to get better and not worse.

00:14:42.154 --> 00:14:51.547
It's time to believe even greater. Put the big boys up on the front line of that football team.

00:14:51.548 --> 00:15:01.528
It's time to put the great defensive backs up there going, "Hey, we're going to stop the run, and they're not going to get the touchdown."That's what you've got to do.

00:15:01.529 --> 00:15:08.287
I probably kicked that too much, but that's why I just feel in my spirit to tell you all it's not time to stop.

00:15:08.288 --> 00:15:16.292
It's not time to give up. It's time to press. I warned you about that.

00:15:16.293 --> 00:15:26.425
So go watch that video of that covered wagon dream that he had. It will bless you.

00:15:26.426 --> 00:15:32.766
It's going to make you go, "Oh my gosh, look at where we are."But look at what he says afterward.

00:15:32.767 --> 00:15:37.685
After the election, there was a flash. And he talked about this.

00:15:37.686 --> 00:15:42.964
He said, "I saw a flash, and everybody was dazed and confused."He warned everybody.

00:15:42.965 --> 00:15:54.081
He said everybody was dazed and confused, and everybody was on the East Coast—they were all in like cots, and they were all trying to find shelter and food and all kinds of stuff.

00:15:54.082 --> 00:16:00.085
What happens? I'm telling you all, the Lord has warned me there's a storm coming.

00:16:00.086 --> 00:16:05.110
I've told you all countless times the Lord has warned me there's a storm coming.

00:16:05.111 --> 00:16:10.451
What is Dana Coverstone? He doesn't directly say it, but he's kind of insinuating something.

00:16:10.452 --> 00:16:17.431
I saw the short-haired blonde-headed lady. So that's a little recap. I saw the short blonde-headed lady with Kamala Harris.

00:16:17.432 --> 00:16:25.116
So if we see all this stuff panning out, it looks like that vision, everything I saw again.

00:16:25.117 --> 00:16:38.004
It looks like I hit it right on the head. Let's just see. We'll see how it pans out.

00:16:38.005 --> 00:16:40.700
They're all going and they're happening almost like dominoes.

00:16:40.701 --> 00:16:47.364
Everything that the Lord showed me about Joe Biden being removed, I warned you all was coming and it happened.

00:16:47.365 --> 00:16:54.808
I said he will not even be running. It will not happen. I told you this last year, 2023.

00:16:54.809 --> 00:17:08.479
I warned you in September of 2023. I told you this was coming. I thought it was coming in November of 2023.

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:16.318
So, I was seeing in the future what the Lord was telling me was coming, but I thought that it was coming that year.

00:17:16.319 --> 00:17:20.879
But no, it's almost a whole year later from what I saw in the spirit.

00:17:20.880 --> 00:17:29.261
I thought this was imminent. That's why I thought it was imminent; I felt it inside. This is what's going to happen this month, this next month.

00:17:29.262 --> 00:17:34.449
I even told my son, "We're going to have an October surprise."Well, we did have an October surprise for Israel.

00:17:34.450 --> 00:17:39.401
It was what the Lord was showing me. I prayed over it and the Lord told me there's going to be a serious event take place.

00:17:39.402 --> 00:17:44.843
I thought it was about America, but I was interceding for Israel and what happened on the Sabbath.

00:17:44.844 --> 00:17:50.558
It was a tragic thing that happened for all those people that were dragged and murdered and everything.

00:17:50.559 --> 00:18:01.495
It was terrible. I was interceding for that. But like I said, it's growing in your gifting; it's growing in what God's called you to do.

00:18:01.496 --> 00:18:08.479
I'm not perfect. I'm learning just like you all. I'm learning how to flow in the gift that God has given me.

00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:13.528
It takes practice. It takes time. It takes maturity. And it's a day-to-day process.

00:18:13.529 --> 00:18:22.331
Just like how a baby learns to walk and pull itself up and crawl and walk and then run and fall.

00:18:22.332 --> 00:18:24.724
They keep falling. You learn. That's how you learn spiritually.

00:18:24.725 --> 00:18:28.496
You just keep picking yourself up. You learn. And that's how we process things.

00:18:28.497 --> 00:18:34.340
So, like I said, this is how I've learned over the course of the years I've done things.

00:18:34.341 --> 00:18:39.773
I just want to encourage you all that good days are happening for the body of Christ.

00:18:39.774 --> 00:18:45.891
Good days are happening for the people who will believe him for miracles, signs, and wonders in these last days.

00:18:45.892 --> 00:18:54.304
This is not a time to bury our head in the sand like an ostrich and say, "Well, I don't want to know anything more that's coming."I try to warn you of these things.

00:18:54.305 --> 00:19:01.566
They said, "What are you telling us all this stuff for? We don't want to hear about the plague that's going to kill 350 million people,"because I believe we can lessen it.

00:19:01.567 --> 00:19:08.624
I believe we can maybe even stop it altogether. I warned you all that we have power and authority.

00:19:08.625 --> 00:19:22.399
If the Lord would have mercy on Sodom and Gomorrah for ten righteous people, and he said he would spare the city. He would spare them.

00:19:22.400 --> 00:19:33.544
When Abraham was interceding for that city, how much more with a new covenant with his son that we have as believers?

00:19:33.545 --> 00:19:53.611
If there's 50,000 righteous in this nation in America or all around the world asking God for him to step in and intervene, how much more would Jesus want to do it for us as blood-washed, born-again children of the most high God?

00:19:53.612 --> 00:20:03.359
How much more would he want to step in for us if he would do it for Abraham and he called him a friend of God?

00:20:03.360 --> 00:20:16.568
And Abraham staggered not at the promise of God through unbelief, but was strong in faith, giving glory to God, being fully persuaded that what he had been promised, he was able also to perform it.

00:20:16.569 --> 00:20:22.939
Ladies and gentlemen, we have to be fully persuaded that God is a God of abundance.

00:20:22.940 --> 00:20:28.022
God is a healer. God is a God of love. We have to be fully persuaded.

00:20:28.023 --> 00:20:33.519
But he brings things and he wants you to intercede on behalf of America.

00:20:33.520 --> 00:20:41.591
What did Jesus tell me when I had the visitation? He said, "Brandon, who will stand in the gap for America?

00:20:41.592 --> 00:20:52.359
Who will intercede for America for what's coming?"I told you, ladies and gentlemen, there is a great storm. Sobering days are coming.

00:20:52.360 --> 00:21:01.535
But I believe as believers, we have power and authority to tread on serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:21:01.536 --> 00:21:09.448
I believe with all my heart that we can speak to the mountain and tell it to be removed and be thou cast in the sea if we shall not doubt in our hearts.

00:21:09.449 --> 00:21:17.997
I believe you shall have whatsoever things you say because faith comes by hearing and hearing by the word of God.

00:21:17.998 --> 00:21:25.578
And as you get that word down inside of you and renew your mind every day, life and death is in the power of your tongue.

00:21:25.579 --> 00:21:29.377
And what you say out of your mouth, you're going to start living tomorrow.

00:21:29.378 --> 00:21:33.478
What you said out of your mouth yesterday, you're living today.

00:21:33.479 --> 00:21:40.127
I'm telling you, the fruit of what you say is what you're going to start living because that's what the Bible says.

00:21:40.128 --> 00:21:44.528
Life and death is in the power of the tongue. You're going to start living it.

00:21:44.529 --> 00:21:50.200
Ladies and gentlemen, if you start speaking blessing over your life instead of curses, you're going to start living a blessed life.

00:21:50.201 --> 00:21:58.639
I believe it. An abundant life, an overflow life, a life full of prosperity and health and healing and wellness for your family.

00:21:58.640 --> 00:22:04.371
But you start cursing your husband and you say, "Oh, he's a no-good so-and-so. Oh, my kids are lazy.

00:22:04.372 --> 00:22:09.873
They don't ever do nothing."You're going to get the manifestation of it because you will have what you say.

00:22:09.874 --> 00:22:20.449
The Bible tells us that you will have what you say. Say something good over your life today, for life and death is in the power of your tongue.

00:22:20.450 --> 00:22:31.918
So, I want to tell you all this. Let's believe today that God is turning things around and we will not see a financial crash crisis.

00:22:31.919 --> 00:22:37.334
It may try to come out and do something, but we can stop it and lessen it.

00:22:37.335 --> 00:22:45.148
We can stop it and the plague. He's warning; the watchman's on the wall.

00:22:45.149 --> 00:22:53.839
"Hello. Hello. Look ahead."And I'm yelling down on the wall, "Hello. Hello everybody. Hey, I'm seeing this in the horizon.

00:22:53.840 --> 00:23:02.688
Pray and obey."Humble yourself before the mighty hand of God and he will exalt you in due time.

00:23:02.689 --> 00:23:09.250
He said, "If my people will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways..."Come on, folks.

